{"tid":2068940,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一場武漢肺炎搞到我進退維谷","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:08:51.000Z","uid":156659,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38a48bf15074683a0e1b92afe3d4344ca790f0a7","tid":2068940,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:57:27.000Z","msg":"依間公司由fg做到依家有4年，23.5K programmer<br />\n之前話今年會升職，我就諗就算佢唔升我，大不了裸辭休息一兩個月先再揾工(唔想一世人non stop咁做野，希望襯後生點都有一次裸辭)<br />\n點知一場武漢肺炎搞到公司咩budget都少晒，例如無headcount請人，有人走都唔會請而係內部揾replacement, 搬office又暫緩，同埋講明我無咁快有得升。<br />\n你話人工都算，但做野方面真係食晒屎，日日都開會晒時間，做嘅野開始急同chur仲有個on9同事成日拖我後腿，依排工作仲有好多屎要執。<br />\n各位連登巴絲有無咩意見比我？<br />\n<br />\n1. 揾第二份工，走人(但就會non stop咁做野)<br />\n2. 繼續做到武漢肺炎無事，之後裸辭再休息一下(但唔知要幾時) <br />\n3. 直接裸辭休息(但無得去旅行)<br />\n4. 其他"},{"pid":"aa5ebac578de3b238bdbdfcec8bae3e7097ae85a","tid":2068940,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8269031a92af5f28d9e24eb397fce559007404ce","tid":2068940,"uid":63750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"有無拍拖，有無儲錢，有無家庭負擔"},{"pid":"a0c855ee5d773622f36690b5348148f1c98d9f45","tid":2068940,"uid":204177,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dc1f72b209aa45c359b4e1116b2f531306dd78","tid":2068940,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8269031a92af5f28d9e24eb397fce559007404ce","tid":2068940,"uid":63750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"有無拍拖，有無儲錢，有無家庭負擔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"有，有，無咩"},{"pid":"059e0db2684939016b3ff0b5680be15bf983c073","tid":2068940,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0c855ee5d773622f36690b5348148f1c98d9f45","tid":2068940,"uid":204177,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-